title: EMC Unity Storage: Status Batteries
agents: emcunity
catalog: hw/storagehw/emc
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 Reports the status of a storage processor battery in an EMC Unity storage system.
 
 The check returns {OK}, {WARN}, or {CRIT} depending on the health state reported by the special agent.
 
 The information is retrieved by the special agent agent_emcunity which uses
 EMC's command line tool uemcli.

item:
 Generated with the "Name" value of the battery in the agent output.
 E.g. "SP A Battery 0"

perfdata:
 None

inventory:
 Automatically configures one check for every battery listed in the agent output.
